<html>
    <header>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/themes/{$THEMENAME}/styles.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/themes/{$THEMENAME}/help.css">
    </header>
    <body>
        <h1>{$node_name}</h1>
        <p align="Justify">Module Peer Information show the list of peer established. This module allow to share DialPlan with other server through Internet.</p>
	<br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img1.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 1</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">SEND REQUEST</b>

	<p align="Justify">To create a connection to access the "New Request" in the Peers Information section and fill the form:</p>
	<br />
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img2.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 2</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul>
	      <li><b style="font-style: italic;">Host Remote:</b> Ip Remote Server to send request.</li>
	      <li><b style="font-style: italic;">Remote Host Secret Keyword:</b> It is the secret key from the server to connect. This key must be sent via email by the server to connect to the your server to create the request.</li>
	      <li><b style="font-style: italic;">Comment:</b> Some comments about request.</li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/><br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img3.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 3</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>The state of the local server on hold: <b style="font-style: italic;">"waiting response"</b></li>
	      <li>The state of the remote server with IP 192.168.5.222: <b style="font-style: italic;">"Requesting connection"</b></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">RECEPTION OF PETITION THE REMOTE SERVER</b>

	<p align="Justify">From the other server will be displayed in the list of peer is the connection that the local server tries to establish with other.</p>
	<br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img4.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 4</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>Local status (Remote Server): <b style="font-style: italic;">"Requesting connection"</b></li>
	      <li>Status of server which makes the request from the server "192.168.3.254": <b style="font-style: italic;">"waiting response"</b></li>
	      <li>Options available with details of the server that performs the connection request from the server "192.168.3.254": <b style="font-style: italic;">"View"</b></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/>
	<p align="Justify">In the "View" could view the server information you want to exchange your dial plan.</p>
	<br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img5.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 5</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">REJECTING THE REQUEST IN THE REMOTE SERVER</b>

	<p align="Justify">In the "Requesting connection" in <b>Figure 4</b> when clicking accessing the following screen:</p>
	<br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img6.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 6</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	<b>Figure 6</b> can display the actions you can make from them are:
	<ul>
	    <li><b style="font-style: italic;">Accept:</b> To accept the request of connection.</li>
	    <li><b style="font-style: italic;">Reject:</b> To reject the request od connection.</li>
	</ul>
	If the action is "Reject" then the server side which done ​​the request will display the following screen:
	</div>
	<br/><br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img7.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 7</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>Local status is rejected: <b style="font-style: italic;">"Request rejected"</b></li>
	      <li>Remote status is rejected: <b style="font-style: italic;">"connection rejected"</b></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">ACCEPTING THE REQUEST IN THE REMOTE SERVER</b>

	<p align="Justify">If the action "Accept" in the <b>Figure 6</b> is selected then the server side which done ​​the request will display the following screen:</p>
	<br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img8.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 8</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>Shows the Mac Address sharing the server with whom you want to connect.</li>
	      <li>Status of the remote server with which you want to connect in this case is disconnected and only need to apply the remote server the action "connect" to establish the connection: <b style="font-style: italic;">"disconnected"</b></li>
	      <li>Action to connect: <b style="font-style: italic;">"Connect"</b></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">CONNECTION SUCCESSFUL</b>

	<p align="Justify">If both servers accept the connection and are in state "connected" then the process is complete and both servers can make call to each other.</p>
	<br/><br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img9.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 9</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>Status <b style="font-style: italic;">"connected"</b> of the local server.</li>
	      <li>Status <b style="font-style: italic;">"connected"</b> of remote server.</li>
	      <li>Action for details of connection: <b style="font-style: italic;">"View"</b></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">DISCONNECTING A PEER</b>

	<p align="Justify">If for some reason you want to disconnect the connection this could be done by entering the screen shown below from the "view" shown in <b style="font-style: italic;">Figure 9</b>.</p>
	<br/><br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img10.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 10</div>
	<br/><br/>

	<b style="font-size: 20px;">DELETING A PEER</b>

	<p align="Justify">If a petition has been rejected you just have to remove it:</p>
	<br/><br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img11.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 11</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>Button of remove peer.</li>
	      <li>Popup of confirmation to remove peer.</li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<p align="Justify">If a connection has been removed then the other server would see the following:</p>
	<br/>
        <div align="center"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/img12.png" border="0"></div>
	<div align="center">Figure 12</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<div>
	Where:
	  <ul style="list-style-type: decimal;">
	      <li>Action to remove the peer.</li>
	      <li>Local Connection Status: <b style="font-style: italic;">"request Deleted"</b></li>
	      <li>Remote Connection Status: <b style="font-style: italic;">"connection deleted"</b></li>
	      <li>Popup of confirmation to remove peer.</li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
    </body>
</html>
